original_title: Peter Frampton Raw: An Acoustic Show
overview: Rock legend Peter Frampton performs on stage in California on his first-ever “completely acoustic tour”. Frampton takes us on a musical journey through his catalogue of over 40 years in this intimate concert. Joined on stage by writing partner, Gordon Kennedy, songs like “Show Me The Way”, “Line On My Face” and “Do You Feel Like I Do” musically stripped down like you’ve never heard before.
title: Peter Frampton Raw: An Acoustic Show
